===美國全國排名===
*奧斯汀德州大學在倫敦[[泰晤士報|泰晤士報]]的全世界大學排名中名列第十五。<ref name="thes">{{cite web|url=http://www.thes.co.uk/worldrankings/ |title=World University Rankings |work=The Times Higher World University Rankings 2005 |publisher=[[The_Times_Higher_Education_Supplement|The Times Higher Education Supplement]] |accessdate=2006-02-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070504114435/http://www.thes.co.uk/worldrankings/ |archivedate=2007-05-04 }}</ref> 根據[[美國國家科學研究委員會|美國國家科學研究委員會]]對研究所普遍性的品質調查，奧斯汀德州大學的七個博士研究科別在全國排名前十，二十二個科系排名前二十五。
*德州大學西南醫學院在2005年為美國排名第17的醫學教育機構。在該校服務的教職員有四名諾貝爾獎得主，是全美最多諾爾獎的醫學院。<sup>来源请求</sup>
*德州大學安德森癌症中心在研究及教學上是全世界最頂尖的癌症研究中心。<ref name="m.d._anderson">{{cite web | url = http://www.mdanderson.org/departments/newsroom/display.cfm?id=90D03116-048A-442D-A3A40E4D0360FABC&method=displayFull&pn=00c8a30f-c468-11d4-80fb00508b603a14 | title = M. D. Anderson Recognized For Contributions in Cancer Care | work = News Room | publisher = [[M._D._Anderson_Cancer_Center|The University of Texas M. D. Anderson Cancer Center]] | accessdate = 2006-02-10 | archive-date = 2006-02-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20060217165348/http://www.mdanderson.org/departments/newsroom/display.cfm?id=90D03116-048A-442D-A3A40E4D0360FABC&method=displayFull&pn=00c8a30f-c468-11d4-80fb00508b603a14 | dead-url = no }}</ref>
